<br>
I'm only level 27, so I have quite a bit of leveling before I can get here. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
It just transfers all your remaining HP into the target, therefore killing you, right? Other than that it's just a normal death?<br>
<br>
I still think this would be cool, but to make it a bit better, why not just make it a 0% exp loss for that death? By the time you'd need to do this, you probably don't have a lot of HP left anyway, so something to make this a bit more effective would be to lessen the penalty for it.<br>
<br>
Just an idea. I plan on using it either way. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=96231">-Occam</a><br>
